headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Get 2X GTA$ and RP on all First Dose Missions from Los Santos Drug Wars
content: The Fooliganz are wreaking havoc on Los Santos as Dax and his group of misfits leave a trail of psychedelic mayhem in their wake. Provide backup, take out rival gangs, and join up with the troupe in First Dose missions to reap Double Rewards this week.
